hint:
カウンタを 2 から始めて 2 ずつ増やすと偶数だけを取り出せます。

```c
int started = 0;
for (int i = 2; i <= n; i += 2) {
    if (started) printf(" ");
    printf("%d", i);
    started = 1;
}
printf("\n");
```

explanation:
## 解説

`i` を 2 から 2 ずつ増やすと偶数を順に得られます。値の間だけに空白を入れるため、最初の値かどうかを `started` で管理します。

```c
int started = 0;
for (int i = 2; i <= n; i += 2) {
    if (started) printf(" ");
    printf("%d", i);
    started = 1;
}
printf("\n");
```

answer_code:
#include <stdio.h>

int main(void) {
    int n;
    scanf("%d", &n);
    int started = 0;
    for (int i = 2; i <= n; i += 2) {
        if (started) printf(" ");
        printf("%d", i);
        started = 1;
    }
    printf("\n");
    return 0;
}
